# Media, image, and document tools
brew "exiv2" # Image metadata manipulation tool. [Exiv2](https://www.exiv2.org/)
brew "ghostscript" # An interpreter for the PostScript language and for PDF. [Ghostscript](https://www.ghostscript.com/)
brew "imagemagick" # Tools and libraries to manipulate images in many formats. [ImageMagick](https://imagemagick.org/)
brew "netpbm" # Toolkit for manipulation of graphic images. [Netpbm](http://netpbm.sourceforge.net/)
brew "pngcheck" # Verifies the integrity of PNG and dump information about PNG image files. [Pngcheck](http://www.libpng.org/pub/png/apps/pngcheck.html)
brew "vbindiff" # Visual binary diff, visually compare binary files. [Vbindiff](https://www.cjmweb.net/vbindiff/)
brew "xpdf" # PDF viewer. [Xpdf](https://www.xpdfreader.com/)

# Web font tools
brew "bramstein/webfonttools/sfnt2woff" # Convert sfnt (TrueType/OpenType) fonts to WOFF. [Sfnt2woff](https://github.com/bramstein/sfnt2woff)
brew "bramstein/webfonttools/sfnt2woff-zopfli" # Convert sfnt fonts to WOFF using Zopfli compression. [Sfnt2woff-zopfli](https://github.com/bramstein/sfnt2woff-zopfli)
brew "woff2" # Web Open Font Format 2.0. [Woff2](https://github.com/google/woff2)
